<html>

<%- include('../includes/head') %>

<body>
  <script>
     var consent=0;
     var q = 1;
     $(document).ready(function() {
      
      $('#question-'+q).show(100);
    })
    function updateConsent(i){
      consent=i;
      if(consent===1){
        showContent('#next-1')
      }else{ // If not visible
        hideContent('#next-1')
      }
    }
  </script>
  <div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="jumbotron">
      <form class="form-horizontal" role="form" method="POST" action="/submit">       

        <div id="question-1" class="section">
          <p style="text-align: center;">
            <b>Step 1 - Prior to the exercise</b>
          </p>
          <br/>
          <p>
            I have completed the pre-physical activity screening, such as the 
            <a target="_blank" href="https://www.acsm.org/docs/default-source/files-for-resource-library/par-q-acsm.pdf">Physical Activity Readiness Questionnaire for Everyone (PAR-Q+)</a>. I have had a proper set-up and a safe area to workout at home.
          </p>
          <div class="form-group">
              <div class="col-sm-8">
                  <input type="radio" name="q-1" value="1" required onclick="updateConsent(1)"> Yes &nbsp;&nbsp;
                  <br/>
                  <input type="radio" name="q-1" value="0" onclick="updateConsent(0)"> No &nbsp;&nbsp;
              </div>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
                  <button id="next-1" name="next" type="button" value="next" class="btn btn-success" style="display: none; " onclick="goNext(1)">Next</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="question-2" class="section">
          <p style="text-align: center;">
            <b>Step 2 - What is your goal?</b>
          </p>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-8">
              <input type="radio" name="q-2" value="Strength" required> Build Muscle: My goal is to build up muscle mass and improve my overall "strongness."
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-2" value="Toning"> Toning Up: My goal is to shape my body up and improve both my strength and cardio health.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-2" value="Cardio"> Loss Weight: My goal is to build up my heart and lung functioning and lose weight.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-2" value="Random"> Random: I do not know my schedule. Please randomly choose one for me!
            </div>
          </div> 
          <br/>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
             <button id="next-2" name="next" type="button" value="next" class="btn btn-success" onclick="goNext(2)">Next</button>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div id="question-3" class="section">
          <p style="text-align: center;">
            <b>Step 3 - What is your time availability?</b>
          </p>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-8">
              <input type="radio" name="q-3" value="Little" required> Little: I can only exercise two to three days each week, less than half an hour each time.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-3" value="Some"> Some: I have time to exercise three to four days each week, roughly half an hour to forty minutes each time.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-3" value="A lot"> A lot: I want to exercise almost every day! That is five days a week, up to an hour each time.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-3" value="Random"> Random: I do not know my schedule. Please randomly choose one for me!
            </div>
          </div> 
          <br/>    
          <div style="text-align: center;">
             <button id="next-3" name="next" type="button" value="next" class="btn btn-success" onclick="goNext(3)">Next</button>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div id="question-4" class="section">
          <p style="text-align: center;">
            <b>Step 4 - What is your exercise level?</b>
          </p>
          <br/>
          <p>
            Please complete the <a target="_blank" href="https://www.ons.org/sites/default/files/Godin%20Leisure-Time%20Exercise%20Questionnaire_070815.pdf">Godin Leisure-Time Exercise Questionnaire</a> and choose one of the following options that best represents your exercise level. The exercise intensity will be automatically generated based on the individual level.
          </p>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-8">
              <input type="radio" name="q-4" value="Beginner" required> Beginner: Less than 14 units. 
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-4" value="Intermediate"> Intermediate: 14-23 units.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-4" value="Advanced"> Advanced: 24 units or more.
              <br/>
              <input type="radio" name="q-4" value="Random"> Random: I do not know my level. Please randomly choose one for me!
            </div>
          </div> 
          <br/>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
             <!-- <button id="next-4" name="next" type="button" value="next" class="btn btn-success" onclick="goNext(4)">Next</button> -->
             <input id="submit" name="submit" type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-success">Next</button>
          </div>
        </div>

          <!-- last -->
          <!-- <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-2">
              <input id="submit" name="submit" type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn btn-success">
            </div>
          </div> -->

          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-2">
              <! Will be used to display an alert to the user>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>  
        
      </form>
      </div>
      <%- include('../includes/footer') %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
